{
  "texts": [
    "This level is useful for tasks in which students may benefit from extra support in developing ideas or improving their work, but in which the final product must be solely humanauthored.",
    "Using GenAI tools at this level may benefit students by allowing them to explore a wider range of ideas and improve the depth or final quality of their work.",
    "Examples of Level 2 activities include:",
    "• Collaborative brainstorming: Students can use AI to generate ideas or solutions to problems.",
    "These ideas can then be discussed, filtered, and refined by students in a collaborative setting."
  ]
}